# This CSV contains satellite: # Each row corresponds to one flight instance with satellite observations
# path: Relative path to the collocation folder
column4: sensing_time: Timestamp of the satellite image acquisition
column5: crs: Coordinate reference system of the satellite image
column6: extent: Spatial extent of the image
column7: visualization_url: URL to visualize the scene quickly (if available)
column8: base_url: Base URL to Google Sentinel-2 dataset (Sentinel-2 only)
column15: longitude: Aircraft longitude at sensing time
column16: latitude: Aircraft latitude at sensing time
column22: x: X coordinate of contrail annotation
column23: y: Y coordinate of contrail annotation
column24: contrail_formation: Boolean flag if contrail formed
column26: out_of_frame_flag: Boolean flag if contrail continues outside image frame
column32: rhl_iagos_error: IAGOS Relative humidity (Liquid Water) Error
column33: rhl_iagos_validity: IAGOS Relative humidity (Liquid Water) Validity
column44: efficiency_PS_IAGOS: PS-computed aircraft efficiency using IAGOS weather data interpolated to sensing time
column45: efficiency_BADA4_IAGOS: BADA 4.2-computed aircraft efficiency using IAGOS weather data interpolated to sensing time
column46: efficiency_PS_ERA5: PS-computed aircraft efficiency using ERA5 weather data interpolated to sensing time
column47: efficiency_BADA4_ERA5: BADA 4.2-computed aircraft efficiency using ERA5 weather data interpolated to sensing time
